{"tid":857566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳孟宏偉妻持香港護照","createTime":"2018-10-11T07:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T07:49:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae476c338b98ea2309f33368fb721326cb2f573f","tid":857566,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181011/20519638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F20519638&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZ4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=83e3db3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F20519638&h=18a556db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181011/20519638</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月11日 <br />\n<br />\n傳孟宏偉妻持香港護照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181011/large/11cf10p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F11cf10p.jpg&h=e66f835a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孟宏偉失蹤後，其妻Grace高調向法國警方求救，被指欲尋政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國公安部前副部長、國際刑警組織前主席孟宏偉落馬案震驚國際，孟妻Grace Meng近日接受外媒訪問時表示，事後曾接到電話威脅，也擔心在中國的家人受連累。<br />\n<br />\n外界除熱議孟宏偉落馬外，也對其嬌妻的背景充滿疑問，有指Grace有香港護照，住在里昂豪宅區。有分析指出，她在法國如此高調，目的是尋求政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181011/large/11cf09p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F11cf09p.jpg&h=a50e5e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孟宏偉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n里昂租豪宅<br />\n<br />\n身在法國里昂的Grace Meng當地時間周二接受美聯社等傳媒訪問時稱，在丈夫9月底失蹤約一周後，曾接到神秘男子電話威脅，對方稱：「你只要聽，不要說話，我們已派了兩組人專門尋找你。我們知你在哪裏。」<br />\n<br />\nGrace又指，自己高調公開丈夫失蹤，已令自己身陷險境，憂慮連累到在中國的家人。她又否認丈夫涉貪，斥責涉貪指控只是中共藉口。在接受CNN訪問期間，孟妻手機響了三次，未知是否中共人員致電。<br />\n<br />\n同時，Grace身份亦惹外界關注，據指她持香港護照，無業，兩年來在里昂最豪華的地區租住豪宅，由於無「駐外人員家屬」身份，其奢侈生活非由國際刑警組織或中國公安部出資。<br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉現年65歲，妻子年輕，兒子僅7歲，疑是再婚。同時，孟妻被指對抗中共，旨在尋求西方政治庇護，孟掌管中國公安國際合作，掌握不少機密，孟妻一旦爆料或對中共造成殺傷力。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n崔永元爆滬公安涉「大欺詐」"},{"pid":"7fa195b403334b309ae40e77e945f7b0fd045b83","tid":857566,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"香港護照就慘啦救你唔到<br />\n坐硬洗頭艇"},{"pid":"16466faaaf69dd16864db38d2a3c6c72838ca7fc","tid":857566,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd9dca67092f0ab2dc2425647ac0fc5139c76a9a","tid":857566,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa195b403334b309ae40e77e945f7b0fd045b83","tid":857566,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"香港護照就慘啦救你唔到<br />\n坐硬洗頭艇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"搵到法國政治庇護就得"},{"pid":"347660835b26c718b8ab1e0f6c6f61c01fde8e2f","tid":857566,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd9dca67092f0ab2dc2425647ac0fc5139c76a9a","tid":857566,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa195b403334b309ae40e77e945f7b0fd045b83","tid":857566,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"香港護照就慘啦救你唔到<br />\n坐硬洗頭艇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"搵到法國政治庇護就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"法國政府出名奶支，庇護都可以隨時為左利益交人。"},{"pid":"9e0dff1660ff4c97836023091d86785ec75cefa7","tid":857566,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"一個之前不斷迫害人地GA罪人竟然依家話自己受迫害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}